Heat oven to 375 degrees. Separate @Cornbread Swirls{11%ounce} into 6 rounds (do not unroll). Place each roll into a greased #muffin cup{}.

Bake for ~{13-17%minutes}, or until golden brown.

Serve warm or bake ahead and reheat briefly in the #microwave{}.

> Looking to round out your Dad's Day meal? We've got just the thing: a deliciously savory-sweet cornbread. You'll probably want to order a few extra packs since this side goes with just about everything.